reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 15, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I like the color and fabric.I am angry that you are selling a shirt that looks made in a middle school home economics class! The seams are poorly done and some stitching is off of the fabric edges. The collar has NO button or hole for one, ALL of the buttons and holes are misplaced and the zig zag AND closing stitches on the edges are very poorly finished, is very roughly done and it looks horrible when you're wearing it!You won't want to wear this poorly made shirt anywhere people will see it. They will feel sorry for you and your lack of sewing prowess!I also bought a dark blue one and the poor sewing is not as visible. Plus, the collar edges, buttons and button holes are properly done!I've washed them so won't return either---because shipping is $7.00!Mili
